name: Anatinopter
description:
Pass through gate after gate for no particular reason. Fine print:
- Beware of the Sun. Solar proximity will void warranty of Flight Harness™.
- Maintain minimum altitude at all times. Contact with terrain will void warranty of Flight Harness™.
- Do not stray too far into the future or past. Contact with the far future will expire warranty of Flight Harness™. Contact with the distant past may render you ineligible for operating Flight Harness™ and other machinery.
